<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="58" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1005,1983]" pageId="2" pageNumber="58">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,286,1005,1029]" pageId="2" pageNumber="58">Etymology.</emphasis>
The generic name is a combination of 
<emphasis box="[724,777,1006,1029]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="58">mira</emphasis>
– (Greek, meaning “special”) and – 
<emphasis box="[1174,1247,1005,1029]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="58">bythus</emphasis>
